summary: This is a preset based on the dragon age 2 character fenris
descriptionHtml:
This is a preset based on the dragon age 2 character known as Fenris. I spent many hours tinkering with the face and hope you guys like it.

Requirements to have this preset:

Racemenu https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/

Elegant Beauty Stunning Eyes Remastered https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/88506/

Kijiko Hair (male pack) https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/55364/ 

DCE - Realistic Male Face https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/38301/?tab=description

I hope you enjoy this preset

Credit to Bioware for creating the Dragon age games and this character that the preset is based on.
author: Eatfist
